{
  "stem": "12868.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'd make a-- a poem, like Yom Kippur [INAUDIBLE], Yom Kippur in this evening.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Like everybody going to shul, only Germans, when the-- the Germans fighting with the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And all of a sudden the Germans coming in in shul, when they found out there's a gym, a-- a spy-- a spy is there hiding in shul.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they asking all the Jewish people to bring out the spy.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "If not, they burn up the shul.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Many ?] people, I make them poem for this, you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Everybody [INAUDIBLE], crying about them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "This is a long long poem to tell this.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But-- but I-- when the Germans, when the Germans say again, if in two minutes, if you don't give up the spy-- they're gonna burn-- there was already kerosene cans, with-- gasoline cans to burn up the synagogue with all the Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Nobody can find the spy there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But one man, 90 years old, he get up.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he say, I am this.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I am the spy.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He was 90 years blind.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And he couldn't talk [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I-- I am the spy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I am the spy.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I [? gone-- ?] I [? gone ?] for you, all of you.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Let them kill me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I'm the spy.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And they took him on a field.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And they-- and they shoot him as a spy.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "When I say the last one is, nobody in the world-- God shows you people like that spy.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "He went for everybody.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "He saved everybody's life.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "It was all for his life. 90 years old.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "That's when everybody cried for him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "In Yiddish-- you just-- I couldn't express this in English.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "But in Yiddish, it is a different poem.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
